'''Vuvrian''' was the native language of the [[Vuvrian/Legends|Vuvrian]] species from [[Vurdon Ka/Legends|Vurdon Ka]]. Most Vuvrians were fluent in both Vuvrian language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], being literate in both languages.

